[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第一",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明教大師臣法賢奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932a28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932a29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時佛在迦毘羅國尼俱陀林中。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932a29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時迦毘羅國有大釋眾而自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我佛世尊，於過去世何處所生？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何姓？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何族？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何因緣？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」而思惟已，告諸眾曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「釋迦世尊，於過去世，何處所生？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何姓？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何族？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何因緣？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等今者欲往佛所而問此義，如佛所說依教受持。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是言已，與大釋眾即往佛所，頭面禮足依位而坐。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時迦毘羅國大釋眾白佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等大釋眾住迦毘羅國精舍之中，而忽思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我佛世尊於過去世，何處所生？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何姓？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何族？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何因緣？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我等不知，今與釋眾來詣佛所而問此義。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊，為我宣說，我等得聞依教受持。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時世尊為斷眾疑，即說此義告釋眾曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我先不欲宣說此義。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有諸魔外道，若聞此事而復謗言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『沙門憍答摩自說其美，所樂即說、非樂不說，有何所益。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時大目犍連現在大眾中，即從坐起，瞻仰尊顏目不暫捨。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「目連！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸釋眾樂聞於我過去之事，所生之處？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何姓？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何族？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何因緣？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今志心而為宣說。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時會中大目犍連默然思惟，經須臾頃收僧伽梨衣安在頭邊，右脇枕臥累足不動入三摩地；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而復觀察世尊過去之世，所生之處，若姓、若族及因緣事，如實了知無其錯謬，即便出定於大眾前復坐本座。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尊者大目犍連告釋眾曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我於三昧觀彼憍答摩往昔之事，世界壞時，彼諸眾生命終之後，而得往生遍靜天中；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生彼天已，諸根圓滿身相端嚴，眾苦不生身心適悅，色相光明騰空自在；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以天甘味而為飲食，壽量長時無中夭者。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時大地，大水所生滿虛空中，猶如大海風吹波浪，如煎熟乳其水清涼，為彼後時一切眾生，所食清淨最上地味。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時大目犍連復告眾言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「當爾劫壞，眾生生遍靜天者，以彼天中福壽俱盡，捨遍靜天生於人間，所生之身亦如天界，身相端嚴諸根無缺妙色廣大，自有身光恒常照曜，長壽喜樂騰空自在。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於其爾時無日月星辰，無歲數月時等，亦無男女眾生之相；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出生地味以為飲食。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是地味甘美細妙，有情食已而生愛著；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於其後時貪味轉盛，忽令身體而得沈重，所有光忽然不見，於是世間普皆黑暗。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時有情見是世間普皆黑暗，種種驚惶心生憂惱，由是世間出現日月及星曜等，始分晝夜及其時候。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是有情壽命長遠無諸病惱，於其地味貪著多者，色相損減而獲醜惡；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪著少者其身色相恒自端嚴，如是隨心分別二相黑白果報。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而彼眾生互相憎嫉而成不善，以不善故，由此地味即便隱沒，以隱沒故，令諸眾生心生熱惱，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『今無所食，深苦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "深苦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』又復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『最上地味云何隱沒？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未來眾生云何得食？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』令生苦惱疲乏之患，而不可知、不可言說。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時大地之中，不久之間即生地餅，其味殊妙馨香甘美，如迦梨尼迦囉花。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而諸眾生食此地餅，充益身體長壽安樂，身相端嚴氣力增盛。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸眾生貪食多者色相損減，貪食少者色相如故無其損減，由此分別二相黑白，而互相非行不善業，令彼地餅隱沒不見。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以不見故，而諸眾生復生苦惱，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0932c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『深苦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "深苦！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』又復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『所生地餅云何隱沒？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其義不知，而諸有情即得飢困疲乏之苦，未來眾生當於何食？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』由是不久為彼眾生復生林藤，其色殊妙香味甘美。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是有情食此林藤，氣力增盛壽量長遠，形色端嚴人相具足。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又彼眾生，貪食多者色相損減，貪食少者色相如故，如是有情分別二相黑白，而互相非行不善業，由是林藤隱沒不見。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既不見已，令諸眾生心生熱惱，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『苦哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苦哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是美味云何隱沒？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其義不知？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等云何而得飲食？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』由是不久大地之中，出生自然上味香稻，其稻依時自然成熟。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時眾生即取食之，亦甚香美，充益肢體壽量長遠。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是爾時食於香稻，漸覺腹內有所妨礙，而即思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『云何除去？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』作是念已即生二根，男女差別形相各異。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時有情於色、香、味展轉愛著，於自親愛而以香花、衣服種種供養，復以軟言慰喻歡喜令彼忻慶；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有眾生於己非愛，即便輕毀種種呵責，或以瓦石互相𩰖打行不善行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又彼眾生所有過去正法今為非法，過去律儀今為非律儀，乃至晝夜時分亦顛倒分別；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人以斗量炭，而為平滿不正之行，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以倒想故正法為邪，由是香稻亦復隱沒。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時大目犍連告釋眾言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「由香稻隱沒故，令彼眾生逐日諸處尋求稻種而欲種之。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有一人，其性慵懶貪著財利，雖有稻種而不能種。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人知已而告之言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝有稻種，與我少分我要種之。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』彼人言曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我有香稻自要受用，汝今若要我即與汝。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後一日、二日，乃至七日却還我稻。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』此人言曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若一日、二日，乃至七日，或未得還，如至半月、一月即得還之。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』作是言已，即自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『自前香稻非種自生，不假勤力自在受用；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今得稻種，須住田野廣施勤力，晝夜相續方得生長。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「如是念已，心生苦惱涕淚悲泣。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『過去之世，所有眾生色相端正，諸根圓滿人相具足，身心適悅身有光明，騰空自在壽命長遠，所食地味猶如天饌；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而於後時，於此美食生貪著故，身即沈重光明即滅，於是世間普皆黑暗。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又彼有情貪食少者身相不減，貪食多者身相損減，由此分別二相黑白，互相輕毀行不善行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是爾時地味即滅，地餅復生，色相殊妙甘美馨香，增益諸根身心適悅，壽命長遠；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪食少者身相不減，貪食多者身相損減，由此分別二相黑白，互相輕毀行不善行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時地餅亦復不見，由此非久復生林藤，色相殊妙其味甘善，亦如天食，充益肢體壽命長遠；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪食少者身相不減，貪食多者身相損減，由此分別二相黑白，互相輕毀行不善行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時林藤亦復不見，於是世間有自然香稻從地出生，其米香美可長四指，依時成熟其味甘美，充益肢體壽量長遠；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是眾生貪愛增故，所有香稻亦沒不見。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故今者求此稻種住於田野，廣施勤力方得成熟。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「雖生稻米其米漸小，於是眾生貪著地利，廣占田野競多種植，而行非法生賊盜想，於他田種復行偷盜。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有一人見是偷米，如是一遍、二遍乃至三遍，而告言曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝自有米何不自用，云何於他而行偷盜？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933b29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從今之後勿更盜米。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』賊聞是言猶不改過，復於後時又行偷盜。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "前人復見而責之曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『前已誡汝勿行偷盜，何故此時又亦作賊？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』即集多人共以責斷。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復於彼時，於眾人中揀一具福德者立為田主，均分田土各令平等，有不依法者令彼調伏。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "田種若熟，輸其少分以賞田主。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是田主受行戒行，安慰世間依法決斷，合調伏者即便調伏。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「由此世間立剎帝利姓，名三摩達多王，王有大臣名為有情；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其王後時生一太子，名為愛子，王有大臣名伊賀迦；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時愛子王生一太子，名曰善友，彼有大臣名帝羅迦；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時善友王復生一子，名曰最上，彼有大臣名阿跋羅建姹；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "最上王有子，名曰戒行，彼有大臣名哆羅惹伽。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其王頂上生一肉靤，其靤柔軟，常以兜羅綿拂拂於肉靤無諸疼痛；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其靤後熟，自然破裂生一童子，福德端嚴，具三十二相，眾所愛重，因以立名名頂生王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "纔下王頂即入內宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時戒行王內宮之中，有六萬宮人各有嬭乳，俱白王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我有嬭乳，願嬭太子。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』由此因緣亦名我嬭王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時世間所有眾生智慧漸增，能細思惟，稱量分別微細之事，或是、或非及工巧等，是故立名號摩努沙。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時六大天子壽命無量，有六大臣：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一名有情；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二名伊賀羅；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三名帝羅迦；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四名阿跋羅建姹；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五名多羅惹伽；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六名摩努惹。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是六大臣，聰明多智，能治世間有大威德。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0933c28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時頂生王於其右股生一肉靤，其靤柔軟，常以兜羅綿拂拂於肉靤離諸疼痛；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後靤熟自然開裂，生一童子，身相端嚴具三十二相，名為尼嚕，有大智慧福德無量，為金輪王統四天下。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「尼嚕輪王於其後時，在左股上亦生一靤，其靤柔軟，常以兜羅綿拂拂於肉靤無諸疼痛；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後還熟，自然開裂生一童子，端正殊妙具三十二相，名烏波尼嚕，智慧深遠福德無量，為銀輪王統三天下。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「烏波尼嚕王還於後時，向右足上生一肉靤，其靤柔軟，亦以兜羅綿拂拂於肉靤無諸疼痛；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後靤熟自然開裂生一童子，身相端嚴具三十二相，名室尼嚕，福慧深厚，為銅輪王統二天下。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「室尼嚕王於左足上有一肉靤，其靤柔軟，以兜羅綿拂拂於肉靤無諸疼痛；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後靤熟自然開裂生一童子，色相端正具三十二相，名摩尼嚕，福慧深厚，為鐵輪王統一天下。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時大目犍連告釋眾言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是王位相繼至今其數極多，如是眾許王有子，名為愛王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愛王有子，名善友王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善友王有子，名最上王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "最上王有子，名戒行王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "戒行王有子，名頂生王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頂生王有子，名尼嚕王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尼嚕王有子，名烏波尼嚕王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "烏波尼嚕王有子，名室尼嚕王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "室尼嚕王有子，名摩尼嚕王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩尼嚕王有子，名嚕唧王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嚕唧王有子，名酥嚕唧王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥嚕唧王有子，名母唧王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "母唧王有子，名母唧鱗捺王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "母唧鱗捺王有子，名阿誐王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿誐王有子，名阿儗囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿儗囉他王有子，名婆儗囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婆儗囉他王有子，名娑誐囉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "娑誐囉王有子，名摩賀娑誐囉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀娑誐囉王有子，名舍矩禰王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍矩禰王有子，名摩賀舍矩禰王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀舍矩禰王有子，名矩舍王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "矩舍王有子，名烏波矩舍王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b02_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "烏波矩舍王有子，名摩賀矩舍王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀矩舍王有子，名酥捺哩舍曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥捺哩舍曩王有子，名摩賀酥捺哩舍曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀酥捺哩舍曩王有子，名鉢囉拏耶王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉拏耶王有子，名摩賀鉢囉拏耶王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀鉢囉拏耶王有子，名鉢囉拏那王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉拏那王有子，名摩賀鉢囉拏那王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀鉢囉拏那王有子，名鉢囉半迦囉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉半迦囉王有子，名鉢囉多波王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉多波王有子，名嚩彌嚕王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嚩彌嚕王有子，名彌嚕摩多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彌嚕摩多王有子，名阿哩唧王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿哩唧王有子，名囉哩唧瑟摩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "囉哩唧瑟摩王有子，名曩哩唧瑟摩多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曩哩唧瑟摩多王有子，名阿哩止娑滿多王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等王子孫相繼，共有一百大國王，皆都布多羅迦城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於最後王生其一王，名降怨王，彼王有大威德能降諸怨，是故名降怨王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是此王子孫相繼帝位不絕，有五萬四千王，都阿喻駄也城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此最後王復生一子，名無能勝王，彼王子孫相繼，帝位相承，有六萬天子，都波羅奈國。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王又生一子，名耨鉢囉娑訶王，子孫相繼有八萬四千王，都緊閉羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名梵授王，子孫相繼有三萬二千王，都賀悉帝曩布里城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名賀悉帝捺多王，子孫相繼有五千王，都怛叉尸羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名娑多黎薩王，子孫相繼有三萬二千王，都烏囉娑大城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934b28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名曩誐曩𡁠曩王，子孫相繼有三萬二千王，都無能大城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名勝軍王，子孫相繼有一萬八千王，都瞻波大城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名龍天王，子孫相繼有二萬五千王，都怛摩黎多城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名為仁王，子孫相繼有一萬二千王，亦都怛摩黎多城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名為海王，子孫相繼有一萬八千王，都難多布里也城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名妙意王，子孫相繼有二萬五千王，都王舍城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名娑多謨努那王，子孫相繼有一百王，亦都波羅奈國。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名大軍王，子孫相繼有一千王，都矩舍嚩帝大城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名海軍王，子孫相繼有一千王，都補多羅迦城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一子，名娑多半尼囉王，子孫相繼有八萬四千王，都矩舍嚩帝城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名摩呬目佉王，子孫相繼有十萬王，亦都波羅奈國。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名摩呬鉢帝王，亦名地主王，子孫相繼有一百王，都阿喻駄大城中。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名持世王，子孫相繼有八萬四千王，都彌體羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於最後王復生一王，名大天王，梵行清淨，子孫相繼有八萬四千王，亦都彌體羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於最後王復生一王，名儞彌王，彼王復生摩娛努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩娛努王復生涅里姹儞彌佉努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅里姹儞彌佉努王復生嚕波佉努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嚕波佉努王復生佉努摩曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佉努摩曩王復生佉努滿多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佉努滿多王復生酥涅里舍王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥涅里舍王復生娑涅里舍王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0934c29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "娑涅里舍王復生酥嚕多細曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥嚕多細曩王復生達魔細曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "達魔細曩王復生尾儞多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尾儞多王復生摩賀尾儞多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀尾儞多王復生尾儞多細曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尾儞多細曩王復生阿輸迦王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿輸迦王復生尾誐多輸迦王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尾誐多輸迦王復生頗羅娑埵王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頗羅娑埵王復生惹羅娑埵王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惹羅娑埵王復生沒度摩囉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沒度摩囉王復生阿嚕拏王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿嚕拏王復生儞扇波帝王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "儞扇波帝王復生里娛王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "里娛王復生商迦囉迦王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "商迦囉迦王復生阿難那王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難那王復生阿那里舍目佉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿那里舍目佉王復生惹那迦王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惹那迦王復生散惹曩佉王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "散惹曩佉王復生惹曩沙婆王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惹曩沙婆王復生案曩播曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案曩播曩王復生鉢囉祖囉曩播曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉祖囉曩播曩王復生阿𡁠多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿𡁠多王復生波羅𡁠多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波囉𡁠多王復生鉢囉底瑟恥多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鉢囉底瑟恥多王復生酥鉢囉底瑟恥多王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥鉢囉底瑟恥多王復生摩賀摩羅王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩賀摩羅王復生嚩賀曩王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嚩賀曩王復生酥摩帝王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "酥摩帝王復生涅里姹嚩賀王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅里姹嚩賀王復生捺捨馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "捺捨馱努王復生設多馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設多馱努王復生曩嚩帝馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曩嚩帝馱努王復生室左怛囉馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "室左怛囉馱努王復生尾𡁠多馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尾𡁠多馱努王復生涅里姹馱努王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "涅里姹䭾努王復生捺捨囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "捺捨囉他王復生設多囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設多囉他王復生曩嚩帝囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曩嚩帝囉他王復生唧怛囉囉他王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唧怛囉囉他王復生涅里姹囉他王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等子孫相繼七萬七千王，都僧迦大城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又最後王復生一王，名阿末麗沙王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼王有子名龍護王，子孫相繼一百王，都波羅奈國。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於最後王生其一子，名訖哩吉王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時迦葉如來、應供、正遍知、明行足、善逝、世間解、無上士、調御丈夫、天人師、佛、世尊出見世間，彼佛世尊為菩薩時，持戒梵行發大誓願求無上覺，於兜率天而為補處，機緣成熟下生於訖哩吉王宮，捨位修行而成佛道。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時訖哩吉王，有一太子名曰善生。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此善生王復生王子，如是子孫相繼有一百王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其最後王復生一子，名迦囉拏王，於其後時生二王子：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一名瞿曇；",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二名婆囉捺嚩惹。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此之王子，愛樂王宮貪於國位，恒自思惟，安慰世間行於王事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時瞿曇王子恒復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『眾生生死沈沒三塗，苦惱輪迴而難出離。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』作是念已，即詣父王稽首拜跪，而白王曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今不樂王宮，欲於山野修習梵行而求出家。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』王即告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝為我子，所有國土及於王位，宰輔大臣如在指掌，何故輕棄而求出家？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』瞿曇白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b21_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我觀三界如幻如化，無其堅實，念念無常，何堪愛樂？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於今日辭王出家。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』王既聞已，知子志意即便聽許。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時山中有一仙人，名訖哩瑟拏吠波野努，於其山間以草為菴居止修行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時瞿曇童子即往彼處，踊躍歡喜五體投地頂禮仙足，而白仙曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我別王宮來於此處奉事仙人，願賜攝受。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如是仙人觀於太子志意堅固，即便攝受。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時童子即於山間，採果給水奉事仙人，如是辛勤累經歲月，師以彼童精勤不退，即為立號亦名仙人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於後父王迦囉拏而乃命終，時弟婆囉捺惹，即紹王位行其國事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時瞿曇仙人知王命終，告本師曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今不能於其山中採果給水，欲往城中而自住止。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』師即告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『瞿曇！",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝先來此善住山野，何故於今却往城邑？",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今去時勿往城內，只於補多落迦城側近寂靜之處卓菴居止，守護諸根精進梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』瞿曇童子聞是語已，即往補多落迦大城之外寂靜之處，卓菴結志崇修梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第一",
        "from": "T03n0191_001:0935c12_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]